Craving highway-style dinner on a Friday night? 🌙🍛
We headed to Pardeshi Family Garden Restaurant on Jamtha Road (serving since 2008!) for that authentic dhaba-style dal tadka and more!

Chilled vibes, a separate party section, and best of all—it’s BYOB! 🍾
We tried sev bhaji, dal tadka, jeera rice, and for the chicken lovers—lollipop & handi chicken.
Maza hi aa gaya! 😋

📍Pardesi  Family  Restaurant, Jamtha Road ka yeh hidden gem is a must-try!

🎯 Activities & Prices:
• Motor Scooter – ₹140/head (one round)
• Motor Boat – ₹120/head (15 mins)
• Rowing Boat – ₹80/head (one round)
• Paddle Boat – ₹120/head (15 mins)

🍴 Also Available:
• Lake View Restaurant
• Lake View Cottages
